dmca.title: Travel Company Alleges Infringement, Asks Google to Delist Site

Attention: User Support, DMCA complaints	

Subject: Digital Millenium Copyright Infringement
I wish to lodge a Digital Millenium Copyright complaint as per the following details.  The infringement was brought to my attention by way of a personal communication from another 
web owner who had their site copied in a similar way

1. The copyrighted work at issue comprises the material appearing on 
http://www.austtravel.com.au

2. The material infringing on the copyright comprises the text, illustrations and images appearing on all pages of the website at http://www.gotofound.com/

3. My email address is: [private]@[private]
